I just walked in there and was barely greeted by a waiter with a miserable look on his face, I asked for a table for 2 and get a clueless look from him. I ask him if they're still open (they're open until 12 and at this point its only 10:40) He calls the manager over and the manager confirms that they are still open but then looks in the kitchen and says "oh he left, sorry" so this place closes at Midnight but apparently they let the chef go home early on a Saturday night. I guess everyone just wanted to go home early tonight. I'm sure that waiter was glad they were closing early!

Franco!!!! I can’t say enough to express the excellent service Franco provided to my party of 31 people. I threw a surprise birthday dinner at Sofia and Franco made the experience a joy. From planning the menu, arranging the tables, displaying the cake and serving,serving serving, Franco and the staff at Sofia were amazing. The food was delicious, served piping hot and the champagne, wine and cocktails were never empty. I cannot thank Franco enough for making our celebration one of the best events we have had. The only negative was the night had to end. I am grateful to have had Franco head my event. Elizabeth Mastro
